---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services — Subtle Somatics" description="Connect with your innate resources through presence-based coaching and energetic somatic modalities for deeper healing." lang="en" altLangUrl="/de/angebote">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <h1>Somatic Coaching Services</h1>
      <p>Connect with your innate resources through presence-based coaching and energetic somatic modalities for deeper healing.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Overview -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="services-overview">
      <div class="service-full">
        <div class="service-full-image">
          <img src="/images/subtle-coaching.png" alt="Subtle Coaching" />
        </div>
        <div class="service-full-content">
          <h2>Subtle Coaching</h2>
          <p>Meet yourself where you are in life right now — at the depth where you are vastly resourced to be with life's complexity.</p>
          <p>In presence-based coaching, we work with the alive, moment-to-moment experience of your body-mind-soul system. This is not talk therapy — it's an experiential exploration of what is present right now: the sensations, emotions, and subtle movements that reveal what is most true for you.</p>
          <p>Through deepening self-contact and gentle inquiry, you begin to untangle inner polarities and encounter the vast resources that live beneath the surface of your habitual patterns. Qualities like courage, tenderness, clarity, and inner strength start to emerge — not as something new, but as something that was always there, waiting to be met.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Deepen your connection to the present moment</li>
            <li>Access innate qualities of strength, love, and presence</li>
            <li>Work with thoughts, emotions, and sensations as doorways</li>
            <li>Cultivate self-contact and inner resourcefulness</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn">Book a session</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-full reverse">
        <div class="service-full-image">
          <img src="/images/spinal-energetics.png" alt="Spinal Energetics" />
        </div>
        <div class="service-full-content">
          <h2>Spinal Energetics</h2>
          <p>A subtle yet powerful modality incorporating sound, touch, movement and music to help the nervous system unwind and get in touch with who you are and your innate qualities more deeply.</p>
          <p>At your core, you're strength, love, radiance and trust — and so much more qualities of resourcefulness. Imagine a treasure trove full of gems — every gem is another nuance of resourcefulness that you can ease into embodying more. It's already there. And often it's covered by tension patterns of different kinds — emotional, physical, mental and spiritual.</p>
          <p>I invite you into a safe and brave space to allow these tension patterns to move and shift — unravelling more and more of who you are, truly.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Feel more mobility and space in your body and mind</li>
            <li>Release emotional charge and stored tension patterns</li>
            <li>Encounter a deeper sense of safety in your body</li>
            <li>Experience profound mind-body-soul integration</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn">Book a session</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Transformative Sessions -->
  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="transform-inner text-center">
      <h2>Transformative Somatic Sessions</h2>
      <p>Engage in sessions that deepen your connection to peace, trust, and your inner resources.</p>
      <div class="transform-grid">
        <div class="transform-card">
          <h3>Individual Sessions</h3>
          <p class="price">&euro;130</p>
          <p class="price-detail">per session &middot; approx. 60 min</p>
          <p>One-on-one sessions tailored to your unique process. Whether you are drawn to presence-based coaching, spinal energetics, or a blend of both, each session meets you exactly where you are.</p>
          <p class="price-note">Available in person (Vienna) and online (Zoom)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="transform-card">
          <h3>Discovery Call</h3>
          <p class="price">Free</p>
          <p class="price-detail">approx. 20 min</p>
          <p>A free introductory conversation to explore whether this work resonates with you. We'll connect, I'll listen to what's alive for you, and together we'll sense into the right next step.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="transform-card">
          <h3>Series of Sessions</h3>
          <p class="price">5 &times; &euro;130</p>
          <p class="price-detail">individual pacing</p>
          <p>Deeper transformation unfolds over time. A series of sessions allows for sustained exploration, integration, and the gradual embodiment of your innate wholeness.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ EN -->
  <section class="section" id="faq">
    <div class="faq-container">
      <h2 class="text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <p class="faq-subtitle text-center">Common questions about the work and what to expect.</p>

      <div class="faq-grid">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What is Spinal Energetics?</summary>
          <p>A subtle yet powerful modality incorporating sound, touch, movement and music to help the nervous system unwind. It works with the body's natural intelligence to release tension patterns — emotional, physical, mental and spiritual — and reconnect you with your innate qualities of strength, love, radiance and trust.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How does Spinal Energetics differ from other energy work?</summary>
          <p>Spinal Energetics works specifically with the spine as a gateway to the body's energetic, emotional and physical layers. Rather than applying external energy, it invites your body's own intelligence to reorganise, release and integrate — through subtle touch, sound and presence.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What can I expect during a session?</summary>
          <p>Sessions typically begin with landing in stillness together. From there, you're invited to tune into spontaneous movements and subtle sensations. I work with gentle contact along the spine, combined with sound and presence. Many people experience states of deep connection, warmth and aliveness.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What are common effects of this work?</summary>
          <p>Common effects include feeling more mobility and space in your body and mind, releasing emotional charge, and encountering a deeper sense of safety in your body. Over time, people often experience greater coherence, inner strength and aliveness.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What is the difference between Subtle Coaching and Spinal Energetics?</summary>
          <p>Subtle Coaching is a presence-based coaching approach that works with thoughts, emotions and sensations as doorways to your innate resources — especially helpful for untangling inner polarities and deepening self-contact. Spinal Energetics is a somatic-energetic modality focused on body-mind integration through touch, sound and movement. Both can be combined or experienced individually.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Who is this work for?</summary>
          <p>This work is for people who want deeper self-connection. Whether you're navigating a life transition, seeking more embodiment and presence, or simply feeling drawn to explore what lies beneath the surface — you're welcome here, just as you are.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Are sessions available online?</summary>
          <p>Yes. Both Subtle Coaching and Spinal Energetics are available online and in person (Vienna, Austria). Online sessions are held via Zoom. In-person sessions offer additional depth through direct contact.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How should I prepare for a session?</summary>
          <p>Come as you are. Wear comfortable clothing and find a quiet space if you're joining online. There's no need to prepare anything specific — we begin where you are.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What about aftercare?</summary>
          <p>After a session, gentle integration is encouraged: journalling, a warm bath, time in nature, grounding, drinking water, and your personal practice. You can always reach out for support between sessions.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What is a Discovery Call?</summary>
          <p>A free introductory conversation to explore whether this work resonates with you. We'll connect, I'll listen to what's alive for you, and together we'll sense into the right next step.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ DE -->
  <section class="section section-cream" id="faq-de">
    <div class="faq-container">
      <h2 class="text-center">Häufig gestellte Fragen</h2>
      <p class="faq-subtitle text-center">Feinspürige Körperarbeit — Antworten auf häufige Fragen.</p>

      <div class="faq-grid">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Was ist Spinal Energetics?</summary>
          <p>Eine feine und zugleich kraftvolle Modalität, die Klang, Berührung, Bewegung und Musik verbindet, um das Nervensystem zu entspannen. Sie arbeitet mit der natürlichen Intelligenz deines Körpers, um Spannungsmuster — emotionale, physische, mentale und spirituelle — zu lösen und dich mit deinen angeborenen Qualitäten von Stärke, Liebe, Ausstrahlung und Vertrauen zu verbinden.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Wie unterscheidet sich Spinal Energetics von anderer Energiearbeit?</summary>
          <p>Spinal Energetics arbeitet gezielt mit der Wirbelsäule als Zugang zu den energetischen, emotionalen und physischen Schichten des Körpers. Anstatt Energie von außen zuzuführen, lädt es die eigene Intelligenz deines Körpers ein, sich neu zu ordnen, loszulassen und zu integrieren — durch feine Berührung, Klang und Präsenz.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Was erwartet mich in einer Sitzung?</summary>
          <p>Sitzungen beginnen typischerweise mit gemeinsamem Ankommen in der Stille. Von dort bist du eingeladen, spontane Bewegungen und feine Empfindungen wahrzunehmen. Ich arbeite mit sanftem Kontakt entlang der Wirbelsäule, kombiniert mit Klang und Präsenz. Viele Menschen erleben tiefe Verbundenheit, Wärme und Lebendigkeit.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Was sind häufige Wirkungen dieser Arbeit?</summary>
          <p>Häufige Wirkungen sind mehr Beweglichkeit und Raum in Körper und Geist, das Lösen emotionaler Ladung und ein tieferes Gefühl von Sicherheit im eigenen Körper. Mit der Zeit erleben viele Menschen mehr Kohärenz, innere Stärke und Lebendigkeit.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Was ist der Unterschied zwischen Subtle Coaching und Spinal Energetics?</summary>
          <p>Subtle Coaching ist ein präsenzbasierter Coaching-Ansatz, der mit Gedanken, Emotionen und Empfindungen als Zugänge zu deinen angeborenen Ressourcen arbeitet — besonders hilfreich beim Entwirren innerer Polaritäten und zur Vertiefung des Selbstkontakts. Spinal Energetics ist eine somatisch-energetische Modalität, die sich auf Körper-Geist-Integration durch Berührung, Klang und Bewegung fokussiert.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Für wen ist diese Arbeit?</summary>
          <p>Diese Arbeit ist für Menschen, die tiefere Selbstverbindung suchen. Ob du gerade einen Lebensübergang navigierst, mehr Verkörperung und Präsenz suchst, oder dich einfach angezogen fühlst, das zu erforschen, was unter der Oberfläche liegt — du bist willkommen, genau so wie du bist.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Gibt es Online-Sitzungen?</summary>
          <p>Ja. Sowohl Subtle Coaching als auch Spinal Energetics sind online und vor Ort (Wien, Österreich) verfügbar. Online-Sitzungen finden über Zoom statt. Vor-Ort-Sitzungen bieten zusätzliche Tiefe durch direkten Kontakt.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Wie bereite ich mich auf eine Sitzung vor?</summary>
          <p>Komm so wie du bist. Trage bequeme Kleidung und finde einen ruhigen Ort, wenn du online teilnimmst. Du musst nichts Bestimmtes vorbereiten — wir beginnen dort, wo du gerade bist.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Was ist mit Nachsorge?</summary>
          <p>Nach einer Sitzung wird sanfte Integration empfohlen: Tagebuch schreiben, ein warmes Bad, Zeit in der Natur, Erdung, Wasser trinken und deine persönliche Praxis. Du kannst dich jederzeit zwischen den Sitzungen für Unterstützung melden.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Was ist ein Kennenlerngespräch?</summary>
          <p>Ein kostenloses Einführungsgespräch, um herauszufinden, ob diese Arbeit mit dir resoniert. Wir verbinden uns, ich höre zu, was in dir lebendig ist, und gemeinsam spüren wir in den nächsten richtigen Schritt hinein.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: var(--color-meteorite-dark);
    color: var(--color-light);
    padding: 10rem 2rem 6rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-hero-inner {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    color: var(--color-light);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .page-hero p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .service-full {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .service-full.reverse {
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .service-full.reverse .service-full-image {
    order: 2;
  }

  .service-full-image img {
    border-radius: 2px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(31, 19, 70, 0.1);
    width: 100%;
  }

  .service-full-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .service-full-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .service-full-content ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .service-full-content li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .service-full-content li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
  }

  .transform-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
  }

  .section-dark .transform-inner {
    padding: 0;
  }

  .transform-inner h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .transform-inner > p {
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .transform-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .transform-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 2px;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .transform-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .transform-card .price {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-light);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .transform-card .price-detail {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .transform-card .price-note {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .transform-card p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* FAQ */
  .faq-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .faq-subtitle {
    color: var(--color-gray);
    margin: 0.5rem auto 3rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(47, 28, 106, 0.1);
  }

  .faq-item summary {
    padding: 1.25rem 0;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-meteorite-dark);
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq-item summary::after {
    content: '+';
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-left: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-item[open] summary::after {
    content: '\2212';
  }

  .faq-item summary:hover {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .faq-item p {
    padding: 0 0 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .service-full,
    .service-full.reverse {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .service-full.reverse .service-full-image {
      order: 0;
    }

    .transform-grid,
    .testimonials-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
